{"tid":1461811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"必需盡快全面輸出自由之火","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:22:43.000Z","uid":107686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f96304cb435845fb33d5f13bfc5cf4432724bf07","tid":1461811,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:21:58.000Z","msg":"多一個朋友好過多一個敵人<br />\n依家內地全面抹黑抗爭運動 証明佢地好驚<br />\n所以我地一定要盡快展開內地文宣 主動出擊<br />\n<br />\n1. 有線有報導指唔少廣州人會睇直播，所以遊行時可以舉下大字報connect 廣州人<br />\ne.g.提下64 講下內地維權、人權 話我地係為中國好 等等<br />\n<br />\n2. 實體翻牆<br />\n有唔少人已經開始寫信寄上去做文宣，澄清下，講下大陸官媒唔可信，叫佢地用VPN等等<br />\n可以參考致內地同胞的公開信<br />\n<br />\n3. 大家發揮下創意 睇下點可以將聲音傳上去<br />\n<br />\n反攻內地 刻不容緩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6170e145363cedb345bc6db54b821c70d14fa345","tid":1461811,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb08c3c5c9a20062c73c2fadea54832fb091572","tid":1461811,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce3f4755c81967d96198b0e458e1ee7c65ee882","tid":1461811,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8aba3c0dceaa275f5d911969a702c16b7f24b2","tid":1461811,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae5227b3cce1c4bb44347e2987463458672e7db","tid":1461811,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}